cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CV 

This paper is about improving neural parsing, which is a natural language processing task. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also discusses generative neural models and model combination, which are topics related to machine learning and artificial intelligence, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) likely categories as well. Additionally, the paper mentions using external data, which could involve computer vision techniques, making cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) a possible category. Finally, the paper proposes an algorithm for direct search, which could involve optimization techniques, making cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) a possible category.
